{
  "texts": [
    "The authors offer a model to distinguish between healthy and early blight-affected tomato leaves.",
    "ResNet and Xception were finetuned for tomato plant leaf classification.",
    "With this refinement process, the system could discriminate between healthy and early blight-infected leaves on tomato plants with an astounding accuracy of 99.95%.",
    "(Kumar and Vani, 2019), the authors analyze several CNN architectures trained to identify diseases in tomato leaves.",
    "The PlantVillage dataset is used for this analysis and consists of 14,903 images."
  ]
}